    "When people are in the same room, their body language, emotions, facial expressions, and non-verbal cues are palpable.",
    "Small talk, informal settings and understanding of the context that surrounds particular business operations are usually missing in ICT enabled meetings.",
    "(also called intermediary, middleman or broker).",
    "Construct teams that include staff with cultural affinity (language, previous experience on multicultural teams).",
    "Facilitation of communication and understanding."
